name: WAGS Atlanta
overview: The lifestyles and real-life relationships of Atlanta's hottest power couples. Viewers get a voyeuristic peek inside the exclusive world of superstar athletes and the women who are hustling and building empires by their side.

episodes.name: Peaches, Prayers and Players
episodes.overview: Kaylin, a former pageant queen, deals with shocking news about her husband. Kesha enlists her friend Telli to help deal with trust issues with her long-term boyfriend, but risks losing him.

episodes.name: The Dating Game
episodes.overview: Kesha deals with a rumor surrounding the legitimacy of her relationship. Kierra's sister ariel is determined to prove her dating prowess, and kaylin tries to cheer up her husband now that his baseball career may be over.

episodes.name: Belles In the Bayou
episodes.overview: Kesha and CJ work on getting their relationship back on track; Niche pushes Andre for a nanny; former pageant girl Kaylin pursues a hosting career that may be over before it starts.

episodes.name: The Ultimate Ultimatum
episodes.overview: Telli seeks commitment when she and Deontay learn they're expecting a baby; Niche pushes Kaylin to pursue the career path she gave up; Ariel and Kierra clash over the family dance business.

episodes.name: Peaches in The Big Apple
episodes.overview: Niche gets a chance to fulfill her lifelong dream at New York Fashion Week; JJ and Kaylin decide to go their separate ways when they both get a once in a lifetime career opportunity; CJ catches Kesha sabotaging his interior designs.

episodes.name: Belles Gone Country
episodes.overview: The girls take a trip to Nashville, and Telli gets much needed perspective on her relationship with Deontay; Brandi steps into the spotlight with a highly acclaimed Ring of Honor wrestling match; Kaylin contemplates starting a family.

episodes.name: Go Your Own Way
episodes.overview: JJ and Kaylin decide to go their separate ways when they both get a once in a lifetime career opportunity
